I like to mix the sugared blackberries with plain greek yogurt. It is a great quick and easy breakfast or light dessert.

Rating: 2
I made this last winter and just came across the recipe again. I concur with brittydear. Made with berries from Trader Joe's, this was just sweet--it had no depth of flavor. It lasted a long time (several months) in the fridge so is a good & easy recipe if you have the right berries.

