Rating: 4
I've made this with both blackberries and raspberries. It's definitely thinner than preserves but tastes very fresh and is SO easy to make. I highly recommend it over vanilla ice cream - yum! I only used 2 cups of sugar the last time I made it and it was sweet enough. I may try to 1/2 the sugar next time.

Rating: 4
What a wonderful, easy way to make homemade preserves! These are more runny than store bought preserves but taste so fresh. I may try it with less sugar next time to make it a bit healthier.